                    is an application that was developed in hopes of motvating individuals to meet there fitness goals by means of friends and easy to comprehend excercises.
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="columns">


<div class="column is-one-fifth">

  <aside class="menu is-one-fifth">
    <p class="menu-label">
      General
    </p>
    <ul class="menu-list">
      <li><a>Dashboard</a></li>
